<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:07:04 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列司机碾压反政府抗议者，造成五人受伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-driver-runs-over-anti-govt-protesters-wounding-five/0000018e-b904-d8b4-a3be-fd0f24610000</link><description>一名反政府抗议者受中伤，另外四人受轻伤。反对党领袖亚伊尔·拉皮德表示，这一事件是“政府煽动的直接结果”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 16:00:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-driver-runs-over-anti-govt-protesters-wounding-five/0000018e-b904-d8b4-a3be-fd0f24610000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方概述了反政府抗议者的法律后果和监禁判决</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-clarifies-rules-for-legal-protesting-at-saturday-nights-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-b8da-d8b4-a3be-fcdf85240000</link><description>上周二在耶路撒冷举行的抗议活动中，警察和抗议者之间的紧张关系达到了顶峰，包括辛贝特（Shin Bet）负责人罗南·巴尔（Ronen Bar）在内的领导人对此表示强烈反对，他称这次抗议活动“超出了可接受的抗议活动的规则”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 15:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-clarifies-rules-for-legal-protesting-at-saturday-nights-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-b8da-d8b4-a3be-fcdf85240000</guid></item><item><title>客运价格上涨后，以色列航空公司提高货运航班价格</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-reduced-competition-israeli-airline-el-al-raised-cargo-flight-prices/0000018e-b800-d50a-a1bf-f86e325e0000</link><description>在以色列航空客运航班价格上涨引起以色列竞争管理局的注意后，进口商现在报告称，该公司已将货运价格提高了 50%；以色列航空表示，价格上涨反映出货运市场价格上涨；货运主管：“归根结底，这是一个供需问题”</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 14:29:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-reduced-competition-israeli-airline-el-al-raised-cargo-flight-prices/0000018e-b800-d50a-a1bf-f86e325e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在西岸枪击事件中受重伤，两名平民受轻伤</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/soldier-seriously-wounded-and-two-civilians-lightly-wounded-in-west-bank-shooting-attack/0000018e-b8ad-d8b4-a3be-fcaf02a40000</link><description>以色列军队认为，成功逃脱的恐怖分子是单独行动，正在搜寻周边地区</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 14:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/soldier-seriously-wounded-and-two-civilians-lightly-wounded-in-west-bank-shooting-attack/0000018e-b8ad-d8b4-a3be-fcaf02a40000</guid></item><item><title>经过四个月的战斗，以色列军队从加沙南部撤军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-withdraws-from-southern-gaza-after-four-months-of-fighting/0000018e-b8ac-db6c-a9ee-fcbc97880000</link><description>军队在谈到即将离开汗尤尼斯的第 98 师时说，“任何能在那里做的事情我们都做了”。以色列国防军部队将留在北部，守卫将加沙一分为二的走廊</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 13:51:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-withdraws-from-southern-gaza-after-four-months-of-fighting/0000018e-b8ac-db6c-a9ee-fcbc97880000</guid></item><item><title>“我想明确紧迫性”：为什么这位巴勒斯坦裔美国医生放弃拜登</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-palestinian-american-doctor-who-came-back-from-gaza-walked-out-on-biden/0000018e-b7e5-d906-a5cf-b7f5d7260000</link><description>泰尔·艾哈迈德医生今年早些时候在加沙汗尤尼斯医院待了几周，他向《国土报》讲述了他在白宫与乔·拜登总统会面时戏剧性的退出，以及他目睹的悲剧：“你只想让它停止”你希望它立即停止&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 13:30:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-this-palestinian-american-doctor-who-came-back-from-gaza-walked-out-on-biden/0000018e-b7e5-d906-a5cf-b7f5d7260000</guid></item><item><title>当MSNBC被问及以色列对哈马斯的资助时，利库德集团部长结结巴巴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-stumbles-when-asked-on-msnbc-about-israeli-funding-for-hamas/0000018e-b82d-d50a-a1bf-f86fbf520000</link><description>政客在面对一名无情地将自己的猎物引向陷阱的敏锐记者时自掘坟墓的情况并不常见，但这正是观众在 MSNBC 的乔·斯卡伯勒 (Joe Scarborough) 采访利库德集团部长尼尔·巴尔卡特 (Nir Barkat) 时亲眼目睹的情况。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 12:33:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-stumbles-when-asked-on-msnbc-about-israeli-funding-for-hamas/0000018e-b82d-d50a-a1bf-f86fbf520000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯谋杀了我的父母。六个月后，以色列的复仇战争威胁着我们所有人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-murdered-my-parents-six-months-later-israels-war-of-revenge-threatens-us-all/0000018e-b7d5-d906-a5cf-b7d55d670000</link><description>以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在加沙陷入了一场战争，这场战争既没有摧毁哈马斯，也没有释放以色列人质。那么它的真正目标是什么？我们以及世界其他国家现在可以做什么来确保这场战争的所有受害者不会白白牺牲？</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 12:19:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-04-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/hamas-murdered-my-parents-six-months-later-israels-war-of-revenge-threatens-us-all/0000018e-b7d5-d906-a5cf-b7d55d670000</guid></item><item><title>辛贝特相信伊朗是向在加沙被扣为人质的以色列妇女家人送葬花圈的幕后黑手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-believes-iran-behind-funeral-wreath-sent-to-family-of-israeli-hostage/0000018e-b804-d906-a5cf-ba94695c0000</link><description>寄给以色列人质莉莉·阿尔巴格（Liri Albag）家人的一封信中写道，“愿她的记忆成为祝福，但每个人都知道国家更重要”。据信她还活着。用于订购鲜花的号码与辛贝特安全部门此前曝光的伊朗影响力活动有关</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 11:24:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/shin-bet-believes-iran-behind-funeral-wreath-sent-to-family-of-israeli-hostage/0000018e-b804-d906-a5cf-ba94695c0000</guid></item><item><title>“我永远不能责怪抵制以色列艺术的人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-never-could-blame-people-who-boycott-israeli-art/0000018e-aa74-d906-a5cf-aaf491670000</link><description>早在 2019 年以色列艺术家 Roee Rosen 被诊断出患有无法治愈的癌症之前，死亡和疾病就一直是他作品的核心。在新展览“如何隐藏自己的痛苦”中，他谈到了这个主题，尽管加沙战争才是伤害他的原因今天</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 11:23:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-04-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/i-never-could-blame-people-who-boycott-israeli-art/0000018e-aa74-d906-a5cf-aaf491670000</guid></item><item><title>六个月后：10 月 7 日和加沙战争如何改变了全球犹太人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-static-ext/.premium/six-months-on-how-october-7-and-the-gaza-war-transformed-jews-across-the-globe/0000018e-6024-d27e-a7af-7aee16960000</link><description>六个月后</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 10:08:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-static-ext/.premium/six-months-on-how-october-7-and-the-gaza-war-transformed-jews-across-the-globe/0000018e-6024-d27e-a7af-7aee16960000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队将在加沙被士兵杀害的人质坟墓上立军事墓碑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-place-military-tombstone-on-grave-of-hostage-killed-by-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018e-b765-d50a-a9ff-ff7fe9fb0000</link><description>去年 12 月，阿隆·沙姆里兹 (Alon Shamriz) 与另外两名人质 Yotam Haim 和 Samer Fuad El-Talalka 在加沙逃离绑架者后被枪杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 08:44:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-to-place-military-tombstone-on-grave-of-hostage-killed-by-soldiers-in-gaza/0000018e-b765-d50a-a9ff-ff7fe9fb0000</guid></item><item><title>四名以色列突击队员在加沙南部丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/four-israeli-commandos-killed-in-southern-gaza/0000018e-b6d1-d50a-a1bf-feff25210000</link><description>枪手从隧道中出现后，士兵们在汗尤尼斯地区搜寻恐怖分子时被杀</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 06:35:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/four-israeli-commandos-killed-in-southern-gaza/0000018e-b6d1-d50a-a1bf-feff25210000</guid></item><item><title>如果没有明确的政治目标，增加加沙援助将无助于以色列军队击败哈马斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/without-declared-goals-increasing-gaza-aid-wont-help-the-israeli-army-defeat-hamas/0000018e-b50d-dc75-afde-f5fd38960000</link><description>以色列国防军在消灭恐怖分子和销毁武器方面取得的战术成功并没有影响加沙战争的结果，如果没有中央政府的分配，增加援助的国际压力也无济于事</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 03:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/without-declared-goals-increasing-gaza-aid-wont-help-the-israeli-army-defeat-hamas/0000018e-b50d-dc75-afde-f5fd38960000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔报道：埃及消息人士预计本周开斋节期间加沙战斗将暂停人道主义行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-east-lebanon-after-israeli-drone-downed-lebanese-security-sources-say/0000018e-b64a-d43f-a18e-bedffd630000</link><description>以色列国防军称，昨天有 14 名士兵受伤，其中 4 名伤势严重 ■ 伊朗官员称，以色列大使馆不再安全 ■ 以色列国防军称，有 30 枚从黎巴嫩发射的火箭落入空旷地区 ■ 以色列国防军突击旅的四名士兵在加沙地带南部的战斗行动中丧生</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Apr 2024 02:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article-live/israel-strikes-east-lebanon-after-israeli-drone-downed-lebanese-security-sources-say/0000018e-b64a-d43f-a18e-bedffd630000</guid></item><item><title>以色列代表团将参加开罗峰会有关加沙人质释放的谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-set-to-join-cairo-summit-on-gaza-hostage-negotiations-with-hamas/0000018e-b50d-d50a-a9ff-ff1f459a0000</link><description>尽管外交消息人士对哈马斯对其要求采取灵活态度的可能性持悲观态度，但外国消息人士表示，内塔尼亚胡决定给予谈判小组有限的决策权，这也阻碍了谈判</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 21:18:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-set-to-join-cairo-summit-on-gaza-hostage-negotiations-with-hamas/0000018e-b50d-d50a-a9ff-ff1f459a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数万人集会反对内塔尼亚胡政府，要求人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-rally-across-israel-against-netanyahus-govt-demand-hostage-deal/0000018e-b4b1-d43f-a18e-befd53c90000</link><description>在特拉维夫，警察和抗议者之间爆发冲突，一名司机拒绝遵守警察命令，冲撞他们，导致五名抗议者受伤。耶路撒冷、海法、贝尔谢巴以及凯撒利亚内塔尼亚胡私人住宅附近也发生了示威活动</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 20:08:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/tens-of-thousands-rally-across-israel-against-netanyahus-govt-demand-hostage-deal/0000018e-b4b1-d43f-a18e-befd53c90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 183 天：美国情报警告伊朗袭击，以色列国防军在加沙找到人质尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-183-u-s-intel-warns-of-iranian-attack-idf-recovers-body-of-hostage/0000018e-b451-d43f-a18e-beddcf530000</link><description>美国消息人士警告称，伊朗将使用“无人机和巡航导弹”发动袭击，以回应大马士革袭击事件 ■ 纽约时报：在内塔尼亚胡的电话中，拜登威胁称，如果以色列不采取行动减少平民伤亡，他将停止对以色列的支持 ■ 以色列国防军：以色列人质埃拉德·卡齐尔的尸体在加沙寻回 ■ 以色列国防军：哈马斯官员在加沙南部被杀 ■​​ 战争开始 183 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 17:23:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-183-u-s-intel-warns-of-iranian-attack-idf-recovers-body-of-hostage/0000018e-b451-d43f-a18e-beddcf530000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队从加沙打捞被谋杀的以色列人质埃拉德·卡齐尔的尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/israeli-army-retrieves-body-of-murdered-israeli-hostage-elad-katzir-from-gaza/0000018e-b393-d50a-a9ff-ff9f85ed0000</link><description>47 岁的卡齐尔于 10 月 7 日在尼尔奥兹基布兹被绑架。以色列国防军在汗尤尼斯的一个墓地发现了他的尸体，并将其送回以色列。他的妹妹是人质家庭运动的关键人物，她指责政府，称如果不是出于政治考虑，“他本来可以获救”</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 14:19:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-04-06/ty-article/israeli-army-retrieves-body-of-murdered-israeli-hostage-elad-katzir-from-gaza/0000018e-b393-d50a-a9ff-ff9f85ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队射杀一名在其土地上诵读《古兰经》的巴勒斯坦牧羊人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-troops-shoot-and-kill-a-palestinian-shepherd-reading-the-quran-on-his-land/0000018e-b001-d906-a5cf-b29596ef0000</link><description>三名士兵向坐在羊圈外的牧羊人扑去。他们把他撞倒，然后其中一人近距离射杀了他。法赫·贾比尔 (Fakher Jaber) 是四个孩子的父亲，他被怀疑卷入了一起可能从未发生过的事件</description><pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 13:24:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-04-06/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/israeli-troops-shoot-and-kill-a-palestinian-shepherd-reading-the-quran-on-his-land/0000018e-b001-d906-a5cf-b29596ef0000</guid></item></channel></rss>